Title: An Act Changing the Name of Malasa Primary School in Malasa, Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Panglima Sarawi Sadalani Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 822
An Act Changing the Name of Malasa Primary School in Malasa, Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Panglima Sarawi Sadalani Primary School
Section 1. The name of Malasa Primary School in Malasa, Municipality of Bongao, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is hereby changed to Panglima Sarawi Sadalani Primary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
